    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-01-22T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-22T08:00:00-05:00" n="138"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d138">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">856d.00/1–2249: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-01-22T14:00:00+01:00"
                            >January 22, 1949—2 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>280. Schuman<note n="1" xml:id="d138fn1">French Minister for Foreign
                        Affairs.</note> said to me last evening, “I beg of you to tell your
                    government that I am most unhappy about Indonesian situation and apprehensive
                    that your policy may in the long run help only the Communists. I know only too
                    well”, he said, “that the Dutch have been stupid, but facing facts and having in
                    mind our situation in Indochina I hope your people will not be too severe with
                    them.”</p>
                <p>I told Shuman that I would transmit his message but at the same time I took
                    occasion again to emphasize our views on the question.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Caffery</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
